  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dd6\u0da7\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca G20 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0db7\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd3 \u0dc0\u0db1 \u0db6\u0dc0 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Putin says he will attend the G20 summit",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Indonesia is chairing the G20 this year, and the United States has been pressured by major Western nations to exclude Russia from the meeting.",
        "The Kremlin says it has accepted an invitation from Russian President Vladimir Putin to attend the G20 summit in Indonesia from November 15 to 16.",
        "Kremlin aide Yuri Ushakov told the media on Monday that the pattern of Putin's participation was not yet clear.",
        "\"Currently, they have been invited to attend in person, but there is a lot of time for that. I hope the epidemic will allow this important forum to be held face to face, I would like to avoid speculation,\" he said.",
        "Indonesia is chairing the G20 this year, and the United States has been pressured by major Western nations to exclude Russia from the meeting.",
        "However, Indonesian President and G20 President Joko Widodo did not cancel the invitation to Russia. In early April, he announced that he would address Ukrainian President Volodymyr Selensky as a guest at the G20 summit and join world leaders.",
        "Widodo is reportedly planning to travel to Russia and Ukraine to meet with the leaders of those countries and call for peace talks this week."
      ],
